headline: Looking at the Narrative for Digital Realty Trust After Guidance Boost and Analyst Updates
summary: Digital Realty Trust stock has recently seen its fair value price target remain steady at $199.19. Subtle shifts in discount rate and revenue growth projections reflect evolving market dynamics. Analysts attribute these updates to solid demand pipelines and a stable, predictable business model, as well as ongoing investor attention to valuation and market presence.
